WEBVTT

01:31.380 --> 01:34.900
=Generation to Generation=

01:35.020 --> 01:37.940
=Episode 37=

02:10.890 --> 02:11.730
- Mr. Mu.
- Mr. Mu.

02:13.410 --> 02:14.290
Most followers

02:14.290 --> 02:16.100
are helping Qingque Sect
heal the wounded

02:16.100 --> 02:16.940
and clean up the mess.

02:17.500 --> 02:18.890
The rest await your orders.

02:19.570 --> 02:20.980
My time is running out.

02:20.980 --> 02:21.820
- Mr. Mu.
- Mr. Mu.

02:21.820 --> 02:23.170
No need to say more.

02:23.890 --> 02:24.980
From now on,

02:27.130 --> 02:29.220
you two will jointly manage the Li Sect.

02:30.540 --> 02:31.380
Gradually open trade

02:32.730 --> 02:34.610
with the Six Sects.

02:35.060 --> 02:36.260
Coexist in harmony.

02:45.380 --> 02:46.730
All plans are

02:46.730 --> 02:47.730
in this handbook.

02:48.380 --> 02:49.290
After I'm gone,

02:49.850 --> 02:51.660
if you clash with the Six Sects,

02:53.660 --> 02:54.980
you can go to Song Yuzhi

02:55.500 --> 02:56.570
to negotiate a solution.

03:05.010 --> 03:05.850
Yes.

03:09.380 --> 03:10.660
For Zhao's future,

03:14.010 --> 03:16.260
I only wish her peace and smoothness.

03:20.100 --> 03:20.980
If

03:23.340 --> 03:24.940
she finds a good person,

03:28.850 --> 03:30.380
please be sure to

03:31.610 --> 03:32.730
protect her.

03:34.290 --> 03:35.130
- Yes.
- Yes.

03:37.100 --> 03:37.940
Go.

04:29.540 --> 04:30.380
Zhao,

04:31.340 --> 04:33.980
the first half of my life was hard.

04:35.140 --> 04:36.140
Surviving

04:36.930 --> 04:38.610
was my only wish.

04:40.020 --> 04:41.490
Not until I met you

04:43.410 --> 04:45.930
did I know the meaning of living.

04:50.020 --> 04:52.700
Like candlelight piercing the darkness.

04:55.580 --> 04:57.810
Like the fragrant curling cooking smoke.

04:59.290 --> 05:00.490
I'm sorry, Zhao.

05:01.580 --> 05:02.420
I broke my promise.

05:04.900 --> 05:07.050
I still used the Disintegration.

05:15.290 --> 05:16.130
Zhao.

05:17.580 --> 05:18.580
We made a pact.

05:21.540 --> 05:22.780
After I die,

05:23.780 --> 05:26.100
bury my ashes under
that tri-colored peach blossoms tree

05:26.100 --> 05:27.810
in Luoying Valley.

05:29.370 --> 05:31.140
That way, whether I become a breeze

05:33.250 --> 05:34.220
or a grain of sand,

05:36.730 --> 05:38.540
I'll always stay by your side.

05:41.100 --> 05:42.220
If one day,

05:43.170 --> 05:44.660
you find another good match,

05:46.780 --> 05:48.730
I'll be truly happy for you.

05:55.140 --> 05:56.610
You won't die.

05:57.730 --> 05:59.050
And I'll never find

05:59.810 --> 06:01.250
another good match.

06:05.900 --> 06:06.740
Zhao,

06:09.220 --> 06:10.730
I owe you so much

06:11.490 --> 06:12.930
in this life.

06:15.930 --> 06:17.540
I hope you don't blame me.

06:18.930 --> 06:20.370
Don't resent me.

06:23.340 --> 06:24.660
Mu Qingyan.

06:26.100 --> 06:27.850
In this life,

06:29.490 --> 06:31.140
you're the only one I ever loved.

06:35.800 --> 06:38.100
Every time I think of
the seven Python Whips you endured.

06:40.490 --> 06:41.330
I know

06:43.290 --> 06:44.850
you took that punishment

06:45.780 --> 06:48.410
to cut ties with me for good.

06:50.020 --> 06:51.340
But in my heart,

06:52.140 --> 06:53.050
it's the opposite.

06:54.020 --> 06:55.220
In my midnight dreams,

06:58.490 --> 07:00.900
I see you covered in blood.

07:03.220 --> 07:04.410
And at that moment,

07:06.810 --> 07:08.220
I know I have no way to escape.

07:13.370 --> 07:14.850
Then don't escape.

07:16.980 --> 07:19.100
We'll never be apart again.

07:45.540 --> 07:46.980
If I have time

07:49.410 --> 07:51.220
to ride the Golden Peng with you

07:52.980 --> 07:54.410
and revisit the Hanhai Mountains,

07:56.580 --> 07:57.420
how nice that would be.

07:59.580 --> 08:00.420
Okay.

08:02.660 --> 08:04.020
I'll go with you.

08:24.340 --> 08:26.170
Zhao, will you go back to
Carefree Chamber with me?

08:29.780 --> 08:30.730
I will.

08:32.770 --> 08:34.730
I'll stay with you

08:34.730 --> 08:36.220
as long as you want.

08:47.980 --> 08:53.020
♪If we never met♪

08:54.410 --> 08:57.900
♪Would there be no longing♪

08:57.910 --> 08:58.750
Zhao.

09:00.930 --> 09:02.980
♪In that fleeting moment♪

09:03.650 --> 09:05.250
You'll look beautiful

09:08.250 --> 09:09.610
in a wedding dress.

09:10.090 --> 09:13.840
♪Countless times♪

09:14.490 --> 09:15.850
When you get better,

09:18.700 --> 09:20.010
we'll get married.

09:20.550 --> 09:22.910
♪Love and hate, scattered in threads♪

09:22.910 --> 09:27.120
♪Intertwined and tangled into lines♪

09:27.620 --> 09:29.520
♪Holding you and me♪

09:29.520 --> 09:33.930
♪Life spreads without boundary♪

09:34.230 --> 09:36.910
♪After parting♪

09:37.410 --> 09:39.690
♪Before death♪

09:40.850 --> 09:45.370
♪We meet no more♪

10:12.300 --> 10:17.210
♪If we never met♪

10:18.120 --> 10:19.050
Zhao.

10:19.050 --> 10:23.830
♪Life is full of hardships♪

10:25.340 --> 10:27.480
♪In dreams♪

10:28.210 --> 10:31.210
♪I become a sleeping lotus♪

10:31.830 --> 10:34.050
♪Before awakening♪

10:34.310 --> 10:37.660
♪I have already lost sleep♪

10:38.270 --> 10:40.760
♪Love and hate, scattered in threads♪

10:40.760 --> 10:43.750
♪Intertwined and tangled into lines♪

10:43.770 --> 10:45.310
Zhao!

10:46.580 --> 10:49.060
Zhao!

10:51.980 --> 10:54.810
♪After this life♪

10:56.650 --> 10:58.180
Zhao!

10:58.690 --> 11:03.330
♪We meet no more♪

11:03.490 --> 11:06.730
Zhao!

11:10.580 --> 11:12.100
Go back and bury your father properly.

11:12.490 --> 11:14.420
From now on,
this manor will depend on you.

11:15.100 --> 11:16.580
If you ever run into trouble,

11:16.890 --> 11:17.730
Luoying Valley

11:17.980 --> 11:19.300
will surely help.

11:19.890 --> 11:20.940
Thank you, Uncle Cai.

11:22.650 --> 11:23.850
About Zhao's matter...

11:23.850 --> 11:25.580
Let's not mention the past.

11:25.940 --> 11:28.370
It's good you've each found

11:29.180 --> 11:30.020
your own happiness.

11:31.100 --> 11:32.650
Siqi Sect has been troubled
for a long time.

11:33.100 --> 11:34.850
Those old folks inside
aren't easy to deal with.

11:35.370 --> 11:36.820
If you can't handle it alone,

11:37.980 --> 11:38.980
don't push yourself.

11:39.820 --> 11:41.580
Come find me at Luoying Valley anytime.

11:43.650 --> 11:44.820
When it comes to arguing,

11:45.250 --> 11:47.180
I have never lost.

11:47.650 --> 11:49.770
Don't worry, Aunt. I won't overdo it.

11:50.940 --> 11:53.370
If it can't be done in a day,
I'll wait a year.

11:53.370 --> 11:56.370
If a year won't do, I'll wait ten.

11:56.370 --> 11:57.650
I have patience.

11:57.650 --> 11:59.530
I'll eventually clean up
Siqi Sect thoroughly.

11:59.530 --> 12:01.420
Give the martial arts world
an explanation.

12:03.700 --> 12:05.180
You want to take a third wife?

12:06.980 --> 12:08.490
Clean up your mind.

12:08.920 --> 12:10.890
There's pure admiration
between men and women too.

12:12.220 --> 12:13.820
Your thoughts are so dirty.

12:13.820 --> 12:15.580
Be careful, I'll tell Xing.

12:17.250 --> 12:18.090
Let's go.

12:18.890 --> 12:20.130
It's about time we head back.

12:23.130 --> 12:23.970
Yeah.

12:24.370 --> 12:25.820
It's about time we head back.

15:19.730 --> 15:20.570
Zhao.

15:38.890 --> 15:40.700
It's like heaven never shuts all doors.

15:41.650 --> 15:42.850
In the end, he made a desperate move.

15:43.650 --> 15:45.250
He used the Disintegration to

15:45.250 --> 15:46.490
force his inner power to surge.

15:47.530 --> 15:49.850
But he'd already passed
all his inner power to you.

15:50.220 --> 15:51.220
Only the Suzi Fragrance poison

15:51.730 --> 15:53.130
remained in his meridians.

15:55.180 --> 15:56.220
That evil technique

15:56.890 --> 15:58.700
actually forced out all the poison.

17:39.620 --> 17:40.810
Why go to such great lengths to

17:41.290 --> 17:42.420
bring Qi Yunke's remains

17:43.010 --> 17:44.490
from the Sinner's Stone Forest?

17:45.570 --> 17:46.700
With Master as company,

17:47.660 --> 17:49.770
I think aunt will be happy.

17:50.140 --> 17:52.420
Qi Yunke did so many bad things
in his life.

17:53.770 --> 17:55.290
Do you think your aunt will be happy?

17:57.980 --> 18:00.010
After my aunt came back
seriously injured,

18:00.010 --> 18:00.940
she refused medicine and

18:01.490 --> 18:02.420
planned to die.

18:03.330 --> 18:05.660
She was afraid
I'd be bullied in the future.

18:05.660 --> 18:06.860
So she forced herself to

18:07.980 --> 18:09.770
teach me martial arts and formations.

18:10.140 --> 18:11.620
And how to behave.

18:12.490 --> 18:13.330
That's how

18:13.490 --> 18:14.900
she got through each day.

18:15.620 --> 18:17.290
She managed to hold on
for over ten years.

18:18.140 --> 18:19.250
During those years,

18:19.660 --> 18:20.620
only master

18:21.380 --> 18:22.980
came to heal aunt every year

18:23.980 --> 18:25.010
and chatted with her.

18:25.660 --> 18:27.180
Whenever she was with master,

18:27.530 --> 18:28.730
my aunt always had a smile.

18:29.490 --> 18:30.330
So

18:31.050 --> 18:32.660
master must be

18:34.090 --> 18:35.770
the most important person to aunt.

18:38.220 --> 18:39.570
Compared to seeking revenge,

18:41.380 --> 18:42.290
this kind of companionship

18:42.810 --> 18:43.900
is the most precious.

18:49.700 --> 18:50.540
This...

18:51.660 --> 18:52.860
belongs to Mu Zhengyang.

18:54.330 --> 18:55.530
Or rather

18:55.530 --> 18:57.180
it's a gift from Ms. Cai
to Mu Zhengyang.

18:59.730 --> 19:00.570
I think

19:00.860 --> 19:01.900
leaving it here

19:02.730 --> 19:04.090
is the best choice.

19:05.530 --> 19:06.370
That's good.

19:06.730 --> 19:07.660
This way,

19:07.660 --> 19:09.940
they can chat and recall the past.

19:15.620 --> 19:16.620
Aunt,

19:16.620 --> 19:17.940
you've stayed in solitude for so long.

19:18.770 --> 19:20.220
It's time for a bit of
warmth and company.

19:21.330 --> 19:22.700
We were once travelers,

19:23.250 --> 19:24.620
drowning in wine-induced cheer.

19:25.090 --> 19:26.290
Since we parted like floating clouds,

19:26.550 --> 19:27.860
ten years have drifted away.

19:28.660 --> 19:29.530
However brilliant

19:29.530 --> 19:31.250
one may be,

19:32.530 --> 19:35.140
however astonishing one's feats

19:35.140 --> 19:35.980
and passions once were,

19:36.380 --> 19:37.250
in the end,

19:38.290 --> 19:39.380
all return

19:41.010 --> 19:41.850
to dust.

19:42.770 --> 19:43.860
Living in this world,

19:44.330 --> 19:45.290
I often wonder

19:46.050 --> 19:47.700
what truly matters most.

19:48.010 --> 19:48.980
Aunt once said

19:49.860 --> 19:51.050
that to live in this world,

19:52.140 --> 19:53.010
what matters most

19:53.620 --> 19:55.180
is to be sensible and joyful each day,

19:56.250 --> 19:58.090
with no shame when looking up or down.

19:59.180 --> 20:00.250
The Yin clan may one day fall.

20:00.940 --> 20:02.140
The Nie clan may vanish too.

20:02.770 --> 20:03.610
We

20:04.980 --> 20:06.010
will never perish.

20:09.700 --> 20:10.540
We

20:11.620 --> 20:12.810
will never perish.

20:16.940 --> 20:18.220
(Breeze)

20:34.420 --> 20:35.570
Aunt!

20:35.570 --> 20:36.620
Master.

20:36.620 --> 20:37.940
This is Breeze.

20:37.940 --> 20:40.140
Uncle Lei asked me to bring it to you.

20:40.140 --> 20:41.420
If you know from the other side,

20:42.570 --> 20:44.140
now we can share a drink again.

21:54.420 --> 21:59.100
(Sunshine Blade Manual)

22:09.500 --> 22:11.820
(Sunshine Blade Manual)

22:19.810 --> 22:20.650
This way, please.

22:23.700 --> 22:25.140
- You're so thoughtful.
- Please.

22:25.140 --> 22:26.420
Here, hand that to me.

22:31.370 --> 22:32.210
Hang it higher.

22:34.770 --> 22:35.810
Elder Yan thinks

22:36.180 --> 22:37.700
the Six Sects just went through turmoil,

22:38.140 --> 22:39.770
so it's a time of transition.

22:40.730 --> 22:42.660
He still wants to persuade
Young Master to go back

22:42.660 --> 22:44.770
to complete Li Sect's great cause
of unifying the Six Sects.

22:44.770 --> 22:45.610
Well now,

22:46.070 --> 22:47.330
Young Master is married just like that.

22:48.730 --> 22:49.570
No.

22:49.770 --> 22:52.250
He's marrying into
this vibrant Luoying Valley.

22:54.380 --> 22:57.180
Young Master!

22:57.180 --> 22:58.940
Look how hopeless you are.

23:00.380 --> 23:01.220
Xing.

23:01.900 --> 23:03.250
Young Master's marriage

23:03.250 --> 23:04.250
is a happy event.

23:04.810 --> 23:05.810
Besides,

23:06.290 --> 23:09.050
none of the new generation of
the Six Sects are easy to deal with.

23:09.050 --> 23:11.140
Like Lord of Siqi Sect, Yang Xiaolan.

23:11.420 --> 23:13.660
Rumor has it she's mastered
the Sunshine Blade Technique.

23:14.010 --> 23:16.050
And Song Yuzhi,
the new Lord of the Qingque Sect.

23:16.490 --> 23:18.530
He reorganized the sect
in just a few months.

23:19.730 --> 23:21.660
If we really fight the Six Sects again

23:21.660 --> 23:22.940
as Elder Yan said,

23:22.940 --> 23:24.050
can we still live in peace?

23:24.490 --> 23:25.330
Yes.

23:25.620 --> 23:26.460
Of course we can.

23:26.760 --> 23:27.620
Dear.

23:27.620 --> 23:29.010
Don't carry such heavy things.

23:31.010 --> 23:31.850
Let me do it.

23:34.050 --> 23:34.900
Alright, coming.

23:36.620 --> 23:38.490
Welcome, Master Shangguan.

23:39.770 --> 23:40.610
My flowers!

23:43.210 --> 23:44.050
You stepped on them.

23:44.050 --> 23:44.890
I...

23:47.530 --> 23:48.660
Where to put Young Master's dowry?

23:49.140 --> 23:49.980
Follow me.

23:51.770 --> 23:52.610
Put it here.

23:57.520 --> 23:58.500
Come on, let's have some tea.

24:02.730 --> 24:03.570
Smiley.

24:04.860 --> 24:05.730
I can't smile.

24:08.770 --> 24:09.730
In three days,

24:10.140 --> 24:11.530
Young Master
will be part of the Cai clan.

24:18.490 --> 24:19.570
So sweet!

24:21.050 --> 24:21.890
Tastes good.

24:22.140 --> 24:24.330
Young Master ordered these
at the fruit shop east of town.

24:24.330 --> 24:25.570
Heard it's improved with licoric.

24:25.570 --> 24:26.570
Too many won't cause internal heat.

24:26.570 --> 24:27.660
I'll take a few jin back

24:27.660 --> 24:29.380
as gifts for the brothers
of Qinglong Altar.

24:29.380 --> 24:30.530
I'll buy a few jin for my wives.

24:30.980 --> 24:32.220
To keep them from being bored

24:32.620 --> 24:33.460
and nagging me every day.

24:34.420 --> 24:35.620
I'm different from you.

24:36.420 --> 24:38.220
I love watching our Xing nag.

24:59.530 --> 25:01.220
This dress style is nice.

25:01.770 --> 25:03.380
But the craftsmanship's a bit rough.

25:03.860 --> 25:04.940
(Tea House)
Needs reworking.

25:04.940 --> 25:06.220
(Inn; Spicy Skewer Shop)

25:09.700 --> 25:10.570
This wax...

25:10.570 --> 25:11.810
Too much of it will produce heavy smoke.

25:12.180 --> 25:14.250
Later, I'll have Shangguan
go back to the Hanhai Mountains

25:14.620 --> 25:16.420
to get some merman wax
from the treasury.

25:16.860 --> 25:17.700
It burns longer

25:17.910 --> 25:18.850
and has a special fragrance.

25:20.050 --> 25:21.180
We can ride the Golden Peng back.

25:21.180 --> 25:22.420
Just in time for the auspicious day.

25:24.240 --> 25:26.220
(Guest: Li Sect, You Guanyue and Xing)
Six Sects and Li Sect

25:26.220 --> 25:27.380
have been peaceful now,

25:27.900 --> 25:29.420
but there are still some old grievances.

25:30.330 --> 25:31.660
We still need to separate their seats

25:32.250 --> 25:33.090
at the banquet.

25:36.220 --> 25:37.060
Zhao,

25:42.010 --> 25:42.850
what are you drawing?

25:43.180 --> 25:44.490
Do you think the clothing shop

25:44.490 --> 25:45.980
should be in front of the shoe shop?

25:46.420 --> 25:47.260
Or behind?

25:47.860 --> 25:48.720
Should the candy shop

25:48.720 --> 25:50.290
be next to the spicy skewer shop?

25:50.660 --> 25:52.220
You're wasting such good time

25:52.900 --> 25:54.570
on this?

25:55.050 --> 25:55.900
Yeah,

25:55.900 --> 25:57.250
it's such a rare chance.

25:58.010 --> 25:58.850
Think about it.

25:59.090 --> 25:59.940
When the time comes,

25:59.940 --> 26:01.700
people from the Six Sects
and Li Sect will all come.

26:01.700 --> 26:02.940
The threshold of Luoying Valley

26:02.940 --> 26:04.090
will be worn out.

26:04.090 --> 26:05.900
All the storytellers across the Jianghu

26:05.900 --> 26:07.090
must shout a line or two.

26:07.700 --> 26:08.540
And what does that mean?

26:09.940 --> 26:11.180
That's our chance.

26:11.770 --> 26:14.050
Whether Xingjia and I
can grow our business

26:14.050 --> 26:15.420
depends on this.

26:15.420 --> 26:16.660
Since Ms. Cai

26:16.660 --> 26:18.420
cares only about doing business

26:18.420 --> 26:20.090
and nothing about marriage,

26:20.620 --> 26:21.570
(Guest)
Then this wedding

26:21.570 --> 26:22.410
doesn't need to happen.

26:24.700 --> 26:25.540
(Guest)

26:57.220 --> 26:59.010
Welcome, welcome!

26:59.010 --> 27:00.290
Wishing you joy and harmony!

27:00.290 --> 27:04.090
Lord Zhou of Peiqiong Manor and his wife
have come to offer their blessings.

27:04.090 --> 27:05.860
Welcome, welcome!

27:05.860 --> 27:07.570
Wishing you joy and harmony!

27:07.570 --> 27:09.290
Welcome, welcome!

27:09.290 --> 27:10.810
Eternal unity!

27:11.490 --> 27:13.050
Lord Zhou and Lady Zhou

27:13.050 --> 27:15.860
wish Mr. Mu and Ms. Cai
a lifetime of harmony!

27:15.860 --> 27:17.010
Welcome, welcome!

27:17.010 --> 27:17.900
Long time no see.

27:18.380 --> 27:19.940
Here, here are the gifts.

27:21.010 --> 27:22.980
Thank you so much.

27:23.860 --> 27:25.220
Gifts from Peiqiong Manor.

27:25.220 --> 27:26.530
A hundred golden silk armors.

27:26.530 --> 27:27.900
A thousand taels of gold.

27:28.120 --> 27:29.140
Just the little gifts from us.

27:30.010 --> 27:33.010
Lord of the Windchaser Manor
and Lady Lingbo

27:33.010 --> 27:34.290
here to offer their congratulations!

27:37.980 --> 27:39.530
Welcome, welcome!

27:39.530 --> 27:41.090
Wishing you joy and harmony!

27:41.090 --> 27:42.900
Welcome, welcome!

27:42.900 --> 27:44.660
Eternal unity!

27:44.660 --> 27:46.330
Welcome, welcome!

27:46.330 --> 27:47.330
Wishing you joy and harmony!

27:47.330 --> 27:48.180
A pair of Ruyi scepters.

27:48.180 --> 27:49.770
A chest of glass lamps.

27:49.770 --> 27:50.770
Lord Dai, please come in.

27:50.770 --> 27:51.610
Dear.

27:53.010 --> 27:53.850
This way.

27:54.620 --> 27:55.620
- Congrats!
- Congrats!

27:55.620 --> 27:56.660
Please, come in.

27:57.050 --> 27:58.780
Xingjia.

27:59.090 --> 27:59.980
Fengchi!

27:59.980 --> 28:00.980
Lingbo!

28:01.530 --> 28:03.090
Come on, please, this way!

28:05.570 --> 28:06.410
Xingjia.

28:06.800 --> 28:07.940
Your hairpin looks really nice.

28:08.650 --> 28:09.490
You look nice too.

28:09.490 --> 28:10.770
Long time no see, Xingjia.

28:11.180 --> 28:12.020
Long time no see.

28:13.700 --> 28:15.300
(Jianghu Fair)

28:15.490 --> 28:16.330
Xingjia.

28:17.050 --> 28:18.090
What's that over there?

28:19.980 --> 28:20.860
The Jianghu Fair.

28:22.290 --> 28:23.130
Here.

28:25.330 --> 28:26.170
Please.

28:27.220 --> 28:28.860
This was all Zhao's idea.

28:28.860 --> 28:31.220
All the delicious food, fine drinks
and useful things

28:31.220 --> 28:33.860
across the Jianghu are here.

28:33.860 --> 28:35.420
(Wine)
This is Peach Blossom Wine from Luoying.

28:35.420 --> 28:37.290
Brewed from the very first blooms
of springtime.

28:37.290 --> 28:39.180
The aroma is rich and sweet.

28:39.180 --> 28:40.620
You can pre-order it next spring.

28:40.620 --> 28:41.460
Also,

28:42.420 --> 28:45.730
the Hanhai Tonic Pills

28:45.730 --> 28:47.490
is a secret recipe passed down
by the Mu clan.

28:47.490 --> 28:49.010
Inherited from the Beichen Founder.

28:55.730 --> 28:56.810
I saw it first.

28:56.810 --> 28:58.220
I got it first.

28:58.220 --> 28:59.660
I saw it first.

28:59.660 --> 29:00.810
But I grabbed it first.

29:00.810 --> 29:02.900
I clearly saw it first!

29:04.010 --> 29:04.850
Xingjia.

29:12.290 --> 29:13.380
Yuzhi has arrived.

29:13.380 --> 29:14.250
I'll go greet him.

29:19.140 --> 29:20.730
Dear.

29:22.570 --> 29:24.010
Dear.

29:25.290 --> 29:26.570
Dear.

29:26.700 --> 29:28.140
Dear.

