Welcome, welcome!

29:58.700 --> 29:59.730
Lord Song.

30:32.090 --> 30:33.180
So beautiful.

30:49.420 --> 30:51.140
May I ask who you are?

30:51.530 --> 30:52.490
Wan Dazhuang.

30:53.050 --> 30:54.700
Wan Dazhuang.

31:00.120 --> 31:01.220
Wan Dazhuang presents his gift.

31:02.380 --> 31:03.730
A piece of thousand-year cold jade.

31:03.730 --> 31:05.180
A snow mountain ganoderma.

31:10.290 --> 31:11.130
Shangguan.

31:11.330 --> 31:12.490
Who is this Wan Dazhuang?

31:13.050 --> 31:13.980
Never heard of him before.

31:14.620 --> 31:15.530
Why did he just leave?

31:18.090 --> 31:19.570
This is my

31:20.180 --> 31:21.980
fiancé I just got engaged to.

31:23.380 --> 31:24.250
His name is Wan Dazhuang.

31:36.140 --> 31:37.770
Eternal unity!

31:41.180 --> 31:42.180
As you wish,

31:43.090 --> 31:44.570
