31:45.860 --> 31:46.700
Take care.

31:47.660 --> 31:48.500
Tao Xiaoshu.

31:49.570 --> 31:51.330
Shopkeeper!

31:52.330 --> 31:53.250
Shopkeeper!

31:53.250 --> 31:54.090
We've got a big deal.

31:54.770 --> 31:55.620
Where's the big deal?

32:04.140 --> 32:04.980
Your hand fan!

32:13.570 --> 32:14.420
Yuzhi.

32:16.900 --> 32:18.490
I'm tied up at Qingque Sect.

32:18.760 --> 32:20.250
