all Guangtian Gate stalls

32:20.250 --> 32:21.770
to you.

32:21.770 --> 32:22.760
Does that count as a big deal?

32:23.250 --> 32:24.090
Open the wine!

32:24.250 --> 32:25.180
I want to talk about

32:25.180 --> 32:26.700
